23 class EventbriteServiceImpl @Inject()(protected val dbConfigProvider: DatabaseConfigProvider,
24                            applicationConfig: ApplicationConfig,
25                            ws: WSClient,
26                            config: EventbriteConfig)
27                           (implicit context: ExecutionContext)
28     extends EventbriteService {
29 
30   val log = Logger("service.eventbrite")
31 
32   val format = new SimpleDateFormat("yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ss")
33 
34   def getEventData(id: String): Future[Option[Model.Event]] = {
35     val request = ws.url(config.url + "/events/" + id + "?expand=venue,category,subcategory,logo")
36       .addHttpHeaders("Authorization" -> ("Bearer " + config.apiKey))
37       
38     val result = request.get()
39 
40     result.map { case x =>
41       log.debug("Got response from eventbrite api: " + x.body)
42       val res = x.json.validate[Model.Event]
43       log.debug(res.toString())
44       res.asOpt
45     }
46   }
47 
48   def getEvent(url: String, login: Login): Future[Option[EventDetail]] = {
49     val t = new URI(url).getPath.split("/")
50     val i = t.indexOf("e")
51     val name = t(i+1).split("-")
52     val id = name.last
53     getEventData(id).map(_.map(x => toEventDetail(x)))
54   }
55 
56   def canImport(url: String, login: Login) = {
57     val uri = new URI(url)
58     val split = uri.getPath.split("/").indexOf("e")
59     (uri.getHost.equals("www.eventbrite.com") || uri.getHost.equals("www.eventbrite.de")) && split >= 0
60   }
61 
62   def toEventDetail(data: Model.Event): EventDetail = {
63     val loc = Location(None, data.venue.name.getOrElse(data.venue.address.address_1.getOrElse("")), Some(data.venue.address.latitude.toFloat), Some(data.venue.address.longitude.toFloat),
64                             data.venue.address.country, data.venue.address.city, data.venue.address.address_1.getOrElse(""), None,
65                             None, None, None, data.venue.address.postal_code)
66 
67     val from = new Timestamp(format.parse(data.start.local).getTime)
68     val to = new Timestamp(format.parse(data.end.local).getTime)
69 
70     EventDetail(None, data.name.text, from,
71                 Some(to), data.description.text,
72                 Organizer(None,"Organizer",-1,None), List(/*TODO Categories*/),
73                 None, loc,
74                 List(TaggedImage(None,None,None,Some(data.logo.url))), 0,
75                 None, None) //TODO Prices
76   }
77 }
